long_desc.thetext:
Your package curlpp failed to build from source in current rawhide.
https://koji.fedoraproject.org/koji/taskinfo?taskID=17712959
For details on mass rebuild see https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_26_Mass_Rebuild

Package uses -Werror so fails on use of deprecated C++03 features:
../../../include/utilspp/functor/Functor.hpp:57:18: error: 'template<class> class std::auto_ptr' is deprecated [-Werror=deprecated-declarations]
It should either stop using -Werror or build with -std=gnu++03
This bug appears to have been reported against 'rawhide' during the Fedora 26 development cycle. Changing version to '26'.
